{"tid":1083404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"硬脫歐了","createTime":"2019-03-29T14:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T15:17:14.000Z","uid":19527,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e999c0812b097e7e1eff1bbb44d239cef1c37d98","tid":1083404,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfa5e4bc3ef434dc8b4c55c1148aa716a23920b","tid":1083404,"uid":214090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982235b6a68aeda564b7ec2fcd7520415b34ba5b","tid":1083404,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"英國國會以286票贊成、344票反對，第三度否決首相文翠珊的脫歐議案。議案內容涵蓋英國脫歐過渡期，以及備受爭議的北愛爾蘭邊境問題等；英國與歐盟未來關係政治宣言，則需另擇日子處理。<br />\n<br />\n英國前外交大臣約翰遜過去已兩次對文翠珊的脫歐議案投下反對票，但他今日在Twitter表示，會「痛苦地」贊成今日表決的議案。文翠珊在表決前的發言中，再呼籲議員支持議案，重申自己「已準備好比原先計劃更早離任」，以為國家和政黨做正確的事。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟上周四（21日）原已同意，若英國國會通過文翠珊的脫歐協議，英國可延至5月22日脫歐；一旦協議被否決，英國必須於4月12日前決定前途，包括是否參加歐洲議會選舉，甚至是無協議脫歐。國會周三（27日）已在無約束力的「指示性投票」中，否決包括二次公投在內的全部8個選項。文翠珊的脫歐議案再被否決後，歐洲理事會主席圖斯克表示，歐洲理事會將在4月10日召開會議相討如何應對。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190329/s00005/1553870519862/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190329%2Fs00005%2F1553870519862%2F&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7QwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=4bd0e13e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20190329%2Fs00005%2F1553870519862%2F&h=59e88059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20190329/s00005/1553870519862/</a>"},{"pid":"c4bcb2d35a2700a67ceec3bb1c406baf3b5f87d7","tid":1083404,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:17:14.000Z","msg":"唔想May姨辭職姐"}]}